nm:output.nm:control_stream:
$PROBLEM 2 compartment fitting $INPUT ID TIME AMT RATE DV MDV EVID WT AGE SEX BUN SCR OCC CRCL COV1 COV2
$DATA ..\..\dmag_with_period.csv IGNORE=@
$SUBROUTINE ADVAN4 ;; advan4 $PK CWTKGONE = WT/81 ;; WEIGHT CENTERED ON ONE CWTKGZERO = WT-81 ;; WEIGHT CENTERED ON ZERO CAGE = AGE/60 ;; AGE CENTERED ON ONE CCRCL = CRCL/85.6 ;; CRCL CENTERD ON ONE CCOV1 = COV1-15.4 ;; COVARIATE 1 CENTERED ON ZERO IOVV = 0 TVV2=THETA(1) *CAGE**THETA(7) *EXP(IOVV) V2=TVV2*EXP(ETA(2)) IOVCL = 0 TVCL= THETA(3) *CWTKGONE**THETA(8) *CCRCL**THETA(9) *EXP(IOVCL) CL=TVCL*EXP(ETA(1))
K=CL/V2 K23=THETA(4)*CWTKGONE**THETA(6) K32=THETA(5)*CWTKGONE**THETA(6) D1=THETA(10) *EXP(ETA(4)) ; infusion only TVKA=THETA(2) KA=TVKA *EXP(ETA(3)) S2 = V2 $ERROR REP = IREP IPRED =F IOBS = F +EPS(1) Y=IOBS $THETA (0.001,100) ; THETA(1) V UNITS = L (0.001, 10) ; THETA(2) KA UNITS = 1/HR (0.001,2) ; THETA(3) CL UNITS = L/HR (0.001,0.02) ; THETA(4) K23 (0.001,0.3) ; THETA(5) K32 (0,0.1) ; THETA(6) K23~WT ; init for K23~WT
(-4,0.8) ; THETA(7) POWER volume ~AGE
(-4,.7) ; THETA(8) POWER clearance~WT
(-4,-0.2) ; THETA(9) POWER clearance~CRCL
(0.01,0.2) ;; D1 THETA $OMEGA 0.1 ; ETA(1) CLEARANCE 0.4 ; ETA(2) VOLUME $OMEGA ;; 2nd OMEGA block 0.1 ; ETA(3) ETA ON KA $OMEGA BLOCK(2) ;; block OMEGA block 0.1 ;; ETA(4) ETA ON ALAG1 0.01 0.1 ;; ETA(5) ETA ON D1 ;; D1 ETA only ;; no iov ON CL ;; no iov ON V $SIGMA 200 ; EPS(1) additive error
$EST METHOD=COND INTER MAX = 9999 MSFO=MSF1 PRINT = 10 $COV UNCOND PRINT=E PRECOND=1 PRECONDS=TOS MATRIX = R
$TABLE REP ID TIME DV EVID NOPRINT FILE = ORG.DAT ONEHEADER NOAPPEND
$PROB SIMULATION FOR CMAX
$INPUT ID TIME AMT RATE DV MDV EVID WT AGE SEX BUN SCR OCC CRCL COV1 COV2 $DATA ..\..\dmag_with_period.csv IGNORE=@ REWIND $MSFI = MSF1 $SIMULATION (1) ONLYSIM $TABLE REP ID TIME IOBS EVID NOAPPEND NOPRINT FILE = SIM.DAT ONEHEADER NOAPPEND
;; Phenotype ;; OrderedDict([('ADVAN', 1), ('K23~WT', 1), ('KAETA', 1), ('V2~WT', 0), ('V2~AGE', 1), ('V2~SEX', 0), ('V2~COV2', 0), ('CL~WT', 1), ('CL~AGE', 0), ('CL~CRCL', 1), ('CL~COV1', 0), ('IOVCL', 1), ('IOVV', 1), ('INITCL', 0), ('ETAD1LAG', 4), ('D1LAG', 1), (' ;; Genotype ;; [1, 1, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 1, 0, 1, 1, 0, 4, 1, 1] ;; Num non-influential tokens = 0
